    "Instruct GPT receives more specific and detailed instructions to produce responses that are not only correct but also aligned with the expectations and needs of the user.ChatGPT: Once the adjustment and optimization through Instruct GPT are complete, the system becomes ChatGPT, which is ready to interact with users.",
    "ChatGPT can receive queries from users and generate responses based on the information learned during training and the adjustments made in the previous stages.User Interaction: When a user submits a query or asks a question, it is sent to the ChatGPT model.",
    "The response process goes through the aforementioned stages, where ChatGPT uses the capabilities of Instruct GPT and the generated outputs to provide an appropriate response to the user.Response to User: Finally, the generated response is sent back to the user.",
    "This interaction cycle can repeat as many times as necessary, depending on the number of queries or questions the user submits.This process illustrates the continuous interaction between the model's various components, ensuring that ChatGPT provides coherent and useful responses based on the user's queries.Fig. 1.",
